1) ci 
    => copy ip of [eth0: default interface] to clipboard and print it out




2) ci <interface>	-- ex: ci tap0
 
    => copy ip, of the chosen interface, to clipboard and print it out




3) ci <interface> m	-- ex: ci eth0 m
    
    => copy mac, of the chosen interface, to clipboard and print it out  



Enjoy
Ali ;)
